{"tid":263514,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來女人真係可以咁絕","createTime":"2017-05-30T05:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T06:12:49.000Z","uid":70900,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1bc46e51bef6398b20e1d970f30ffc1e0301301","tid":263514,"uid":70900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:40:12.000Z","msg":"事源係小弟既女友前晚去左飲酒唔理我<br />\n所以我嬲嬲地講分手<br />\n跟住佢就道出自己原來同我一齊後<br />\n一直對我只得好感<br />\n由始至終<br />\n佢都係迫自己投放感情落我度<br />\n根本唔愛我<br />\n而且覺得我地唔夾<br />\n明明之前我地仲相處得好好<br />\n係毫無預兆既情況下<br />\n我落得咁既收場<br />\n可能有人會話又係我講分手先 抵死<br />\n但係即使我唔講 <br />\n佢心中有個咁既諗法 都唔會行得遠<br />\n最後我想講<br />\n如果俾我重頭開始過<br />\n我一定會令你愛上我<br />\n對唔住"},{"pid":"24b89289f4fcf80c260c1daa81f0d209510391a6","tid":263514,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:41:55.000Z","msg":"搵到另一個佢更加鐘意既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打 女死女還在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60a551ea1a22dc249b5fbb0ddb4d03733cd58ac","tid":263514,"uid":14479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:42:12.000Z","msg":"去飲個酒冇理到你就講分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d19db9ed62741deda6c870087d7f6e32ef76fa58","tid":263514,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a4b6b9704409bbed6745b93c29f35c90b582fb","tid":263514,"uid":64884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:43:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去飲個酒冇理到你就講分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能之前已前積埋積埋好多嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7114048143debc5a451b276a90537867c7ad6a30","tid":263514,"uid":70928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:43:54.000Z","msg":"飲酒既女人早飛早著啦 <br 